title: Road netwok in Haiti: Data from UN MANUSTAH
name: Road netwok in Haiti: Data from UN MANUSTAH
description:
The poly shapefile shows road network across Haiti. Some records have descriptions such as the condition of the road segment as well whether its Principal, Secondary or just a track. 
Look elsewhere on GC for Major Road Network across Haiti as well detailed road netwok in Port Au Prince.
